{
  "texts": [
    "Preprocessing is essential when the quantity of high-quality labeled data is constrained and acquiring additional examples is costly and labor-intensive.",
    "Consequently, it should be regarded as a significant concern in medical analysis, especially in the early diagnosis of Alzheimer's disease.",
    "Maintenance of data can be used for tasks like testing and training data.",
    "Extraction of data is needed for the two steps above.",
    "Taking away the attributes is an easy way to make the data less multidimensional."
  ]
}